title: The Top Performer's Guide to Leadership
description:
Business needs good leaders. Of all the skills a top performer can master, this may be the most important.

The Top Performer's Guide to Leadership shows top performers how to lead in a way that is impactful and authentic. This short, effective guide is perfect for managers to give to employees learning this essential skill.

In this guide, top performers will discover:

Why leadersip is important
What people look for in leaders
How to inspire and get results

...and much more
